<header><bold>Guess who - Rules</bold></header>


In this game you will hold the phone on your forehead and a name will appear on the screen. You team will try to explain who this is and you'll guess. If your right then you turn the phone down and a new name will appear. This will award your team 1 point.


If you or the team members don't know or want to pass on the person you turn the phone up and a new person will come up. This will deprive your team 1 point.